{"tid":1363321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"第日城新巴係咪要叫公交車","createTime":"2019-07-25T06:44:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T10:45:27.000Z","uid":154784,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"187115af968770d7354866e475c1a88020784f01","tid":1363321,"uid":154784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T06:44:22.000Z","msg":"彭博：新創建考慮以3億美元 出售城巴、新巴等資產<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報道，新創建考慮出售城巴、新巴等資產，亦已經與包括招商局集團在內的潛在買家進行會談。報道又指，賣資產行動仍屬初期，未有最後決定。新創建回覆《香港01》查詢時表示，集團不時收到不同的商業計劃，目前沒有協議出售城巴及新巴資產。對於市場猜測，集團不作評論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/355717/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A-%E6%96%B0%E5%89%B5%E5%BB%BA%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E4%BB%A53%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E5%9F%8E%E5%B7%B4-%E6%96%B0%E5%B7%B4%E7%AD%89%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F355717%2F%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%258D%259A-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2589%25B5%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E4%25BB%25A53%25E5%2584%2584%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%2585%2583-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2594%25AE%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B7%25B4-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E7%25AD%2589%25E8%25B3%2587%25E7%2594%25A2&d=9aIS%2Fhk2hxf5w8hb7WAMUQRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=a465e8c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/355717/%E5%BD%AD%E5%8D%9A-%E6%96%B0%E5%89%B5%E5%BB%BA%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E4%BB%A53%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E5%9F%8E%E5%B7%B4-%E6%96%B0%E5%B7%B4%E7%AD%89%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2</a>"},{"pid":"a6b2e14272bc8c679b2fccb16e83ac46fd38c07e","tid":1363321,"uid":154669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:09:27.000Z","msg":"之前仲話城新巴幾有良心咁耐先加次價，原來係為賣比中資舖路，連巴士都就染紅，睇黎離一國一制不遠矣"},{"pid":"2a3aff21e1bae8fc75efc05cf070d8927e1b4c75","tid":1363321,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T08:18:03.000Z","msg":"香港公交集団"},{"pid":"c